    public class TimeAwareNode
extends ctu.nengoros.time.AbstractTimeNode
    This node does the similar thing as: @see org.hanns.demonodes.pubsub.MinMaxFloat, but the resulting minimum and maximum values multiplies by current simulation time in seconds.
